[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Delivered : cancel
Delivered --> OnHold : process
Delivered : entry / log cart
OnHold --> Shipped : reject
Shipped --> Cancelled : approve
Shipped : entry / log cart
Cancelled --> Active : cancel
Cancelled : entry / log cart
Cancelled --> OnHold : revert
Active --> [*]
